Hi Archer,  I would like a custom module for the CMS wysiwyg editor to enable me to create content with collapsible headings.  Something like the below but enabled as a module in the wysiwyg editor.
[1:11 PM] Basically this javascript but in a HubL module that I can pull into a template like an RTF.   Is that a project you would consider?  I plan to follow this with a migration of our current website content into an updated mobile friendly template but this is an immediate need.      <!DOCTYPE html>
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
&lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
.collapsible {
  background-color: #777;
  color: white;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 18px;
  width: 100%;
  border: none;
  text-align: left;
  outline: none;
  font-size: 15px;
}

.active, .collapsible:hover {
  background-color: #555;
}

.content {
  padding: 0 18px;
  display: none;
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: #F1F1F1;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Collapsibles&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A Collapsible:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;button type="button" class="collapsible"&gt;Open Collapsible&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Collapsible Set:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;button type="button" class="collapsible"&gt;Open Section 1&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;button type="button" class="collapsible"&gt;Open Section 2&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;button type="button" class="collapsible"&gt;Open Section 3&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;div class="content"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;script&gt;
var coll = document.getElementsByClassName("collapsible");
var i;

for (i = 0; i &lt; coll.length; i++) {
  coll[i].addEventListener("click", function() {
    this.classList.toggle("active");
    var content = this.nextElementSibling;
    if (content.style.display === "block") {
      content.style.display = "none";
    } else {
      content.style.display = "block";
    }
  });
}
&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
